        <mxCell id="enote" value="Approach B: intermediate crop node keeps every node ≤5 parents (RxInfer exact cap). Sum rule + product rule + MaxEnt CPTs + Dirichlet learning. Calibratable target proposition, e.g. P(≥N cropland/people affected in b within horizon). NO action node — action stays with national DRM." style="text;html=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;align=left;fontColor=#b85450;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1340" y="596" width="250" height="110" as="geometry" /></mxCell>

